1
00:00:50,240 --> 00:00:50,960
General.

2
00:00:51,680 --> 00:00:53,810
Let the Little Princess rest in peace.

3
00:00:54,440 --> 00:00:55,080
No.

4
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:57,290
Ling'er isn't dead yet.

5
00:00:58,680 --> 00:00:59,920
She is just too tired.

6
00:01:01,520 --> 00:01:03,250
She'll be fine after some rest.

7
00:01:06,760 --> 00:01:08,289
Yunyuan, put Ling'er down.

8
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:32,729
Luckily, we made it in time.

9
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,210
Ling'er.

10
00:01:37,000 --> 00:01:37,720
Ling'er.

11
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:39,960
That's great.

12
00:01:41,880 --> 00:01:42,940
It's not that easy.

13
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:46,410
What do you mean?

14
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:49,800
The Seven-Colored Camellia can only gather Ling'er's soul,

15
00:01:49,800 --> 00:01:51,479
but it cannot gather her spirit.

16
00:01:51,479 --> 00:01:52,759
You mean,

17
00:01:54,160 --> 00:01:56,420
there is no way to save Ling'er, is there?

18
00:01:56,800 --> 00:01:58,360
There is only one last way.

19
00:01:59,880 --> 00:02:01,200
Dragon Lord, tell me.

20
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,330
What should I do?

21
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,890
You can take my life.

22
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:07,520
Take Ling'er back first. We'll discuss it later.

23
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:09,800
As long as the Seven-Colored Camellia in her arms isn't moved,

24
00:02:09,800 --> 00:02:10,800
she will be fine.

25
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:12,400
It's just that...

26
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:14,480
she will sleep forever.

27
00:02:17,120 --> 00:02:17,840
Ling'er.

28
00:02:19,600 --> 00:02:21,160
I will definitely save you.

29
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:41,690
Dragon Lord.

30
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:43,760
Please tell me.

31
00:02:46,200 --> 00:02:47,960
How exactly can I save Ling'er?

32
00:02:52,200 --> 00:02:54,730
I have consulted the clan's ancient records.

33
00:02:54,880 --> 00:02:58,140
Ling'er sacrificed her own divine soul to the Spirit Pearl

34
00:02:58,440 --> 00:02:59,700
to protect our people.

35
00:03:00,400 --> 00:03:01,640
To wake Ling'er up,

36
00:03:02,440 --> 00:03:04,370
the Spirit Pearl must be repaired.

37
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:08,520
How can the Spirit Pearl be repaired?

38
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:10,520
Only by finding the ancient treasure,

39
00:03:10,520 --> 00:03:11,780
the Qiankun Cauldron,

40
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:14,400
can the Spirit Pearl perhaps be repaired.

41
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:16,060
But this Qiankun Cauldron...

42
00:03:16,240 --> 00:03:19,120
during the Great War between Immortals and Demons ten thousand years ago,

43
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,320
it was lost.

44
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,460
No matter how hard,

45
00:03:23,280 --> 00:03:24,340
no matter how long,

46
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:27,579
I will find the Qiankun Cauldron.

47
00:03:29,079 --> 00:03:30,400
I will save Ling'er.

48
00:03:31,600 --> 00:03:33,920
The Dragon Clan has suffered this calamity.

49
00:03:33,920 --> 00:03:35,650
Everything needs rebuilding.

50
00:03:36,200 --> 00:03:37,560
I cannot leave.

51
00:03:38,440 --> 00:03:40,970
Finding the Qiankun Cauldron to save Ling'er

52
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,600
can only be entrusted to you.

53
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,760
I have temporarily sealed Ling'er's soul

54
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,920
inside the Seven-Colored Camellia.

55
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:01,520
But it cannot last long.

56
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,640
You must, every so often,

57
00:04:03,720 --> 00:04:05,960
inject spiritual power into the camellia

58
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,600
to nourish Ling'er's soul.

59
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,050
I will announce to the world

60
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:14,080
that for the crime of failing to protect the Little Princess,

61
00:04:14,080 --> 00:04:16,079
you are expelled from the Dragon Clan.

62
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,600
The Spirit Pearl is shattered.

63
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:19,480
But we don't know if other forces

64
00:04:19,560 --> 00:04:21,290
are coveting the Spirit Pearl.

65
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:23,340
For the safety of you and Ling'er,

66
00:04:24,080 --> 00:04:26,160
this is safer.

67
00:04:27,600 --> 00:04:30,060
I will protect the Seven-Colored Camellia.

68
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:31,770
I will protect Ling'er.

69
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,800
I only hope that one day,

70
00:05:01,960 --> 00:05:03,800
when the camellia blooms,

71
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:07,640
my Ling'er can return.

72
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:18,640
General, I'm coming with you.

73
00:05:18,640 --> 00:05:19,320
Yueying.

74
00:05:19,960 --> 00:05:20,890
Why are you here?

75
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:22,680
This journey is fraught with danger.

76
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:24,440
I can't let you risk your life with me.

77
00:05:24,440 --> 00:05:26,720
General, when we formed our alliance,

78
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,280
we swore to live and die together.

79
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:30,520
Now that the Little Princess is in a coma from saving you,

80
00:05:30,520 --> 00:05:32,480
I am duty-bound to save her.

81
00:05:32,560 --> 00:05:34,220
Naturally, I must go with you.

82
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,320
Besides, keeping you safe

83
00:05:36,320 --> 00:05:37,780
is also my heart's desire.

84
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:40,290
Alright.

85
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,760
I am Yunyuan.

86
00:05:53,159 --> 00:05:55,220
I implore the Flower God for answers.

87
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:05,600
Hey, hey!

88
00:06:05,880 --> 00:06:07,320
Take it away! Take it away!

89
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,600
You scoundrel!

90
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:09,560
How dare you!

91
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,930
You chose the hard way, Flower God.

92
00:06:12,200 --> 00:06:13,080
Don't blame me.

93
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:16,000
Though you have lived for ten thousand years,

94
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:18,260
you are still bound by the laws of nature.

95
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:19,800
You still cannot

96
00:06:20,160 --> 00:06:21,090
withstand fire.

97
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,040
You...

98
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,500
You scoundrel, don't push it!

99
00:06:26,200 --> 00:06:27,000
Speak.

100
00:06:27,440 --> 00:06:28,720
What do you want from me?

101
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:29,880
Do you know

102
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:32,480
about the Qiankun Cauldron?

103
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,200
Kid,

104
00:06:34,200 --> 00:06:36,040
why are you looking for the Qiankun Cauldron?

105
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:37,300
You just need to tell me

106
00:06:37,680 --> 00:06:38,920
where it is.

107
00:06:40,120 --> 00:06:40,800
Hey!

108
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,600
I'll talk! I'll talk!

109
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:45,520
Move that fire away!

110
00:06:51,880 --> 00:06:52,600
Kid,

111
00:06:53,520 --> 00:06:54,850
I can see your true form.

112
00:06:54,920 --> 00:06:56,360
You're a Flood Dragon, aren't you?

113
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,560
The Qiankun Cauldron

114
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:59,400
is a holy artifact of the Phoenix Clan.

115
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:03,040
Guarded for generations by the descendants of the ancient Yuanfeng.

116
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:05,040
Never mind if you can find it,

117
00:07:05,400 --> 00:07:06,960
even if you did,

118
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:10,330
it clashes with your Flood Dragon bloodline.

119
00:07:10,600 --> 00:07:11,840
You wouldn't be able to claim it.

120
00:07:11,840 --> 00:07:13,440
That's none of your concern.

121
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,120
Just tell me

122
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,290
where the Qiankun Cauldron is.

123
00:07:17,720 --> 00:07:18,640
Hey, hey!

124
00:07:18,720 --> 00:07:20,280
I'll talk, okay?

125
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,440
Take it away!

126
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:23,520
I was just trying to be nice.

127
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,680
I didn't want you to throw your life away.

128
00:07:25,680 --> 00:07:27,010
Why are you so stubborn?

129
00:07:30,640 --> 00:07:32,159
The Qiankun Cauldron

130
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:35,159
was originally in Qiwu Forest, in the center of the Phoenix Clan's territory.

131
00:07:35,159 --> 00:07:37,280
But ten thousand years ago, a lightning tribulation struck.

132
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,680
The Phoenix Clan was wiped out,

133
00:07:38,680 --> 00:07:40,680
and the Qiankun Cauldron vanished.

134
00:07:41,240 --> 00:07:42,280
Qiwu Forest

135
00:07:42,320 --> 00:07:44,320
turned into a barren Stone Forest.

136
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,760
In the last ten thousand years,

137
00:07:45,760 --> 00:07:47,920
no one has heard of the Qiankun Cauldron.

138
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,580
Where is the Stone Forest now?

139
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:52,800
The Stone Forest is in Kunmi, thousands of miles away.

140
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:54,440
Thank you.

141
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:55,720
Yueying.

142
00:08:04,760 --> 00:08:05,440
General.

143
00:08:06,080 --> 00:08:08,480
There's nothing but black rocks around here.

144
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,740
Could that flower spirit have lied to us?

145
00:08:15,080 --> 00:08:16,340
It's not above ground.

146
00:08:17,680 --> 00:08:18,740
It's underground.

147
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:26,320
Why is it that the deeper we go,

148
00:08:26,320 --> 00:08:27,760
the more parched I feel?

149
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:36,860
Rumor has it the Qiankun Cauldron is an object of pure Yang.

150
00:08:37,640 --> 00:08:38,320
Perhaps

151
00:08:38,880 --> 00:08:40,280
we're in the right place.

152
00:08:42,919 --> 00:08:43,480
Let's go.

153
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,960
With my cultivation,

154
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,410
ordinary water and fire

155
00:08:53,440 --> 00:08:54,570
could never harm me.

156
00:08:54,600 --> 00:08:55,800
There is something odd about this fire.

157
00:08:55,800 --> 00:08:56,480
Be careful.

158
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,120
Yes, General.

159
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,810
There is something down there.

160
00:09:14,280 --> 00:09:15,360
What petty thieves

161
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:17,480
dare to steal my clan's holy relic?

162
00:09:25,440 --> 00:09:26,640
If this were the past,

163
00:09:26,720 --> 00:09:29,600
I'd beat you until your own mother wouldn't recognize you.

164
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,960
Big words.

165
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,920
I am the Divine Bird, Qingluan.

166
00:09:32,920 --> 00:09:34,160
An ancient divine beast,

167
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,920
descendant of the Primordial Phoenix.

168
00:09:35,920 --> 00:09:36,600
General,

169
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,820
that object wrapped in black aura

170
00:09:39,160 --> 00:09:40,820
must be the Qiankun Cauldron.

171
00:09:41,280 --> 00:09:41,810
Correct.

172
00:09:42,040 --> 00:09:42,880
We found it.

173
00:09:43,680 --> 00:09:44,400
Next,

174
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,860
we must find a way to subdue it.

175
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:49,220
You want to subdue the Qiankun Cauldron?

176
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:52,920
The Qiankun Cauldron is a holy relic of my Phoenix Clan.

177
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:54,250
With just the two of you,

178
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,120
you are daydreaming.

179
00:09:56,440 --> 00:09:57,160
Oh?

180
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:58,760
Do you have a way?

181
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,000
Of course.

182
00:10:00,560 --> 00:10:01,640
Tell me the details.

183
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:04,100
Why should I tell you just because you asked?

184
00:10:05,280 --> 00:10:06,280
It hurts! It hurts!

185
00:10:06,280 --> 00:10:07,600
Total destruction of your soul,

186
00:10:07,600 --> 00:10:08,840
or tell the truth.

187
00:10:09,440 --> 00:10:10,570
The choice is yours.

188
00:10:11,040 --> 00:10:11,800
I'll talk!

189
00:10:14,400 --> 00:10:15,360
I... You...

190
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:21,400
In the beginning of the primordial chaos,

191
00:10:21,400 --> 00:10:25,120
heaven and earth birthed three divine beasts: the Ancestral Dragon, the Primordial Phoenix, and the Qilin.

192
00:10:25,120 --> 00:10:26,400
During the Great War of the Wilds,

193
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,060
the three divine beasts fell.

194
00:10:28,760 --> 00:10:29,960
Hey, get to the point.

195
00:10:30,480 --> 00:10:31,800
A gentleman uses his words, not his fists!

196
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,800
You really are...

197
00:10:33,360 --> 00:10:34,560
I'm not talking anymore.

198
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,160
Miss,

199
00:10:35,520 --> 00:10:38,580
my General needs the Qiankun Cauldron to save someone.

200
00:10:39,160 --> 00:10:40,620
Please tell us the method.

201
00:10:41,160 --> 00:10:42,420
Who do you want to save?

202
00:10:48,840 --> 00:10:49,720
My General...

203
00:11:00,360 --> 00:11:02,320
That's so touching.

204
00:11:02,920 --> 00:11:06,240
I haven't heard such a touching story in a long time.

205
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,840
I am just telling the truth.

206
00:11:10,320 --> 00:11:12,320
There's no need for such a reaction.

207
00:11:13,480 --> 00:11:14,320
I've decided.

208
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:16,800
I will tell you how to subdue the Qiankun Cauldron.

209
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:18,520
If you are willing to help, Miss,

210
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:19,680
no matter the difficulty,

211
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,140
I, Yun, will pay any price.

212
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:28,420
Try using the blood from my heart.

213
00:11:33,440 --> 00:11:34,200
Now!

214
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,680
Quickly, use your divine consciousness to communicate with it.

215
00:11:35,680 --> 00:11:38,000
Its hostility has been suppressed by my heart's blood.

216
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:38,720
Hurry!

217
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,400
The Qiankun Cauldron lies within the Earth Core Fire.

218
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:47,120
It requires powerful spiritual energy as a guide,

219
00:11:47,120 --> 00:11:49,240
and one's own primordial spirit as a vessel.

220
00:11:49,240 --> 00:11:52,760
Otherwise, it will never leave the Earth Core Fire.

221
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:54,340
No matter what,

222
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:56,560
I must obtain the Qiankun Cauldron.

223
00:12:00,680 --> 00:12:03,810
He actually possesses the Ancestral Dragon bloodline.

224
00:12:09,160 --> 00:12:09,840
General!

225
00:12:10,520 --> 00:12:12,120
If he cannot suppress the Qiankun Cauldron,

226
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:13,880
everything he has done will be in vain.

227
00:12:13,880 --> 00:12:14,940
You can't help him.

228
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:18,960
General!

229
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,920
If you have something to say, Miss,

230
00:12:33,920 --> 00:12:35,120
please speak freely.

231
00:12:35,560 --> 00:12:37,560
I'll be honest with you then.

232
00:12:37,800 --> 00:12:40,880
Back then, my primeval spirit was placed in the Qiankun Cauldron for nourishment.

233
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:42,680
But during the great war,

234
00:12:42,840 --> 00:12:46,320
the Cauldron absorbed a massive amount of demonic energy and fell into the Earth Ruins.

235
00:12:46,320 --> 00:12:48,880
My primeval spirit inside hasn't recovered yet.

236
00:12:48,880 --> 00:12:50,760
If it is taken out now,

237
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:52,480
it might be harmful to me.

238
00:12:53,320 --> 00:12:54,040
So...

239
00:12:55,000 --> 00:12:55,930
What do you mean?

240
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,690
I want to be by your side.

241
00:12:57,800 --> 00:12:59,200
I want to follow you forever.

242
00:12:59,200 --> 00:13:00,600
Considering I used my own heart's blood

243
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,240
to help you tame the Qiankun Cauldron,

244
00:13:02,240 --> 00:13:02,680
You...

245
00:13:02,720 --> 00:13:03,980
Mind your words, Miss.

246
00:13:04,440 --> 00:13:06,440
I don't have those feelings for you.

247
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:08,730
No, no, no. That's not what I meant.

248
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,240
I meant that we...

249
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,000
Oh, no.

250
00:13:12,440 --> 00:13:13,080
No, no.

251
00:13:14,080 --> 00:13:16,480
I don't have those feelings for you either.

252
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:17,440
I mean...

253
00:13:18,760 --> 00:13:21,490
Why is it getting harder to explain the more I try?

254
00:13:23,960 --> 00:13:24,490
General.

255
00:13:24,840 --> 00:13:26,640
Miss Qingluan means that

256
00:13:26,800 --> 00:13:27,880
she wants to travel with us

257
00:13:27,880 --> 00:13:30,040
so that once her primeval spirit is fully nurtured,

258
00:13:30,040 --> 00:13:31,900
she can retrieve it immediately.

259
00:13:32,400 --> 00:13:34,400
Right. That's exactly what I meant.

260
00:13:34,800 --> 00:13:36,520
If you find it inconvenient,

261
00:13:36,680 --> 00:13:39,520
I can dress as a man and be your guard.

262
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:41,680
In that case,

263
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:45,660
let us address each other as brother and sister from now on.

264
00:13:45,800 --> 00:13:46,640
Brother,

265
00:13:46,920 --> 00:13:48,200
please accept my bow.

266
00:13:52,280 --> 00:13:53,200
Qingluan,

267
00:13:53,960 --> 00:13:55,160
we are away from home.

268
00:13:55,840 --> 00:13:57,920
There's no need for such formalities.

269
00:13:57,920 --> 00:14:00,160
Brother, since we are family now,

270
00:14:00,400 --> 00:14:02,560
there is something I need to tell you.

271
00:14:03,920 --> 00:14:04,850
Don't tell me...

272
00:14:04,920 --> 00:14:05,320
You...

273
00:14:05,760 --> 00:14:07,560
what else are you hiding from us?

274
00:14:07,680 --> 00:14:09,920
The Qiankun Cauldron has been in the Earth Ruins for thousands of years.

275
00:14:09,920 --> 00:14:13,050
And it was tainted by demonic energy even before it fell.

276
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:15,440
If the Camellia and the Spirit Pearl

277
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:17,600
are kept inside for nourishment like this,

278
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,480
I fear they will be corrupted by the malevolent energy.

279
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:21,210
It is not a long-term solution.

280
00:14:22,560 --> 00:14:24,620
Since we found the Qiankun Cauldron,

281
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:27,020
I will find a way to solve these problems.

282
00:14:27,120 --> 00:14:29,250
Then, Brother, where are we going now?

283
00:14:30,560 --> 00:14:32,720
To restore the Spirit Pearl with the Cauldron,

284
00:14:32,720 --> 00:14:34,840
we need abundant spiritual energy from heaven and earth.

285
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:36,320
Years ago, during the war,

286
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,480
I heard

287
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:39,500
there is a Spirit Spring in Kunmi.

288
00:14:39,680 --> 00:14:42,160
The spiritual power there is extremely abundant.

289
00:14:42,160 --> 00:14:43,680
It is suitable for restoring the Spirit Pearl.

290
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:44,560
Besides,

291
00:14:44,800 --> 00:14:46,660
Ling'er has always missed Kunmi.

292
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,440
If she wakes up

293
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:50,130
and finds herself in Kunmi,

294
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:52,120
she will surely be happy.

295
00:15:05,560 --> 00:15:06,760
The Kunmi in my memory

296
00:15:07,160 --> 00:15:08,640
was rich in heavenly treasures.

297
00:15:08,640 --> 00:15:10,680
It was an ideal place for all living things to grow.

298
00:15:10,680 --> 00:15:11,480
But now,

299
00:15:11,960 --> 00:15:13,760
demonic energy runs rampant.

300
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:16,120
There is no spiritual energy to speak of.

301
00:15:16,120 --> 00:15:18,520
Those are resentments from the human race.

302
00:15:18,560 --> 00:15:20,320
And those black things on the ground,

303
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,440
are malevolent energy from the Earth Ruins.

304
00:15:22,440 --> 00:15:23,880
Let's find a place to stay first.

305
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:25,010
Once we settle down,

306
00:15:25,240 --> 00:15:27,840
we will clear out this demonic and malevolent energy.

307
00:15:27,840 --> 00:15:29,640
It will benefit the people here.

308
00:15:30,880 --> 00:15:32,640
Ling'er cares for the common people.

309
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:34,970
If she wakes up and sees Kunmi like this...

310
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,480
She would be sad.

311
00:15:52,040 --> 00:15:52,880
Qingluan.

312
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:54,570
Brother, I don't feel well.

313
00:15:57,080 --> 00:15:58,280
Rest here for a while.

314
00:15:58,920 --> 00:15:59,840
General.

315
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:01,930
Do you feel any discomfort?

316
00:16:02,080 --> 00:16:03,000
I feel fine.

317
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:04,090
Strange.

318
00:16:04,480 --> 00:16:06,340
We went up the mountain together.

319
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:08,210
Why do I feel no discomfort?

320
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:14,240
Ling'er, is that you?

321
00:16:14,960 --> 00:16:16,220
Are you protecting me?

322
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:36,400
Ling'er, you like it here.

323
00:16:37,000 --> 00:16:38,200
You want to save them.

324
00:16:40,480 --> 00:16:41,200
Yueying.

325
00:16:41,520 --> 00:16:43,050
Find a place to stay nearby,

326
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:44,130
and get settled.

327
00:16:44,640 --> 00:16:45,920
You mean...

328
00:16:46,840 --> 00:16:48,300
Ling'er likes this place.

329
00:16:48,600 --> 00:16:49,660
So I will stay here.

330
00:16:50,000 --> 00:16:52,600
Perhaps Ling'er has regained consciousness.

331
00:17:04,119 --> 00:17:05,960
Once the Spirit Pearl is restored,

332
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,280
Ling'er will wake up.

333
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:13,160
Brother.

334
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,440
You can't go on like this.

335
00:17:15,440 --> 00:17:17,240
Your body is reaching its limit.

336
00:17:18,480 --> 00:17:20,599
I can definitely restore the Spirit Pearl.

337
00:17:20,599 --> 00:17:21,760
If something happens to you,

338
00:17:21,760 --> 00:17:22,839
what will she do?
